node.text:
“𝙄𝙩’𝙨 𝙖𝙡𝙡 𝙖𝙗𝙤𝙪𝙩 𝙘𝙤𝙣𝙛𝙞𝙙𝙚𝙣𝙘𝙚”

From 🩰 to ⚽️, @martinarosucci takes us through what it means to be a woman and her journey in football. 

#ConfidenceMakesUsDoEverything #JuventusWomen
